text: Rogelio Enrique San Francisco Cobo, better known as Quique San Francisco (10 March 1955 – 1 March 2021) was a Spanish actor and comedian. He was born in Madrid. His career began in the 1960s. In 1965, he started his television career with Televisión Española 's show Santi, botones de hotel.Por fin, en TVE, una 'serie' para chicos San Francisco's best known movie works were Colegas (1982), Navajeros (1980) and El pico (1983). San Francisco died on 1 March 2021 at a Madrid hospital from sepsis caused by pneumonia, aged 65. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1955 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Deaths from sepsis Category:Deaths from pneumonia Category:Spanish movie actors Category:Spanish television actors Category:Spanish stage actors Category:Actors from Madrid Category:Spanish comedians
